fect on constructs and undead.  All other creatures within 30 feet of her that can hear must make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw.  On a failure, a creature drops to 0 hit points.  On a success, a creature takes 10 (3d6) psychic damage.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null}],"_Reactions":[],"_Legendaries":[],"Title":"","STR":1,"DEX":14,"CON":10,"INT":12,"WIS":11,"CHA":17,"proficency":2,"Speed":"0 ft., fly: 40 ft. (hover)","AC":"15","HP":"58 (13d8)","CR":{"Index":5,"CR":"2","profBonus":2,"ArmorClass":13,"AttackBonus":3,"SaveDC":13,"LowHP":86,"HighHP":100,"XP":450},"CreatureName":"Banshee","CreatureSize":"Medium","CreatureType":"Undead","CreatureAlign":"Chaotic Evil"}